documentation of the manual prompt-tuning. the final prompt parameters were evaluated by two experts from foresight and NLP
With an interrater reliability of 100% we went for:

        prompt=prompt,
        max_tokens=38,
        temperature=0.9,
        top_p=0.5,
        frequency_penalty=1.9,
        presence_penalty=1.9,

Which has shown to generate full sentences, realistic future scenarios and a high amount of creativity in GPT 3.5 text-davinci-003.
